   Southland Approaches 2 Crucial Dates
   In Plan to Rearrange $1.8 Billion in Debt
   ----
   By Karen Blumenthal
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
06/04/90
</DATE>
